{"title_page": "Ireland at the Olympics", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2014}}\n{{Use Irish English|date=September 2014}}\n\n{{infobox country at games\n| NOC = IRL\n| NOCname = [[Olympic Federation of Ireland]]\n| games = Olympics\n| year = \n| flagcaption = \n| oldcode = \n| website = {{url|olympics.ie}}\n| location = \n| competitors = \n| sports = \n| flagbearer = \n| rank = \n| gold = 9\n| silver = 10\n| bronze = 12\n| officials = \n| appearances = \n| app_begin_year = \n| app_end_year = \n| summerappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Ireland|competition=Summer Olympics|begin_year=|end_year= }}\n| winterappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Ireland|competition=Winter Olympics|begin_year=|end_year= }}\n| seealso = {{flagIOC|GBR}} (1896\u20131920)\n}}\n\nA team representing '''Ireland''' has competed at the [[Summer Olympic Games]] since [[1924 Summer Olympics|1924]], and at the [[Winter Olympic Games]] since [[1992 Summer Olympics|1992]]. The [[Olympic Federation of Ireland]] (OCI) was formed in 1922<ref name=\"ocihistory\"/> during the [[Provisional Government of the Irish Free State|provisional administration]] prior to the formal establishment of the [[Irish Free State]]. The OCI affiliated to the [[International Olympic Committee]] (IOC) in time for the Paris games.<ref name=\"ocihistory\"/> There has been controversy over whether the team represents the [[Republic of Ireland]] or the entire [[Ireland|island of Ireland]], which comprises both the Republic and [[Northern Ireland]].<ref name=\"sullivan\"/>\n\n== Medal tables ==\n{{See also|All-time Olympic Games medal count}}\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n=== Medals by Summer Games ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!Games\n!Athletes\n|style=\"background:gold; width:3.7em; font-weight:bold;\"|Gold\n|style=\"background:silver; width:3.7em; font-weight:bold;\"|Silver\n|style=\"background:#cc9966; width:3.7em; font-weight:bold;\"|Bronze\n!style=\"width:4em; font-weight:bold;\"|Total\n!style=\"width:4em; font-weight:bold;\"|[[Olympic medal table|Rank]]\n|-\n|align=left|1896\u20131920 || colspan=6| ''as part of {{flagIOCteam|GBR}}''\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1924}} || 49 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1924 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1928}} || 29 || 1 || 0 || 0 || '''1''' || [[1928 Summer Olympics medal table|24]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1932}} || 8 || 2 || 0 || 0 || '''2''' || [[1932 Summer Olympics medal table|16]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1936}} || colspan=6| ''did not participate''\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1948}} || 72 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1948 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1952}} || 19 || 0 || 1 || 0 || '''1''' || [[1952 Summer Olympics medal table|34]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1956}} || 18 || 1 || 1 || 3 || '''5''' || [[1956 Summer Olympics medal table|21]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1960}} || 49 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1960 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1964}} || 25 || 0 || 0 || 1 || '''1''' || [[1964 Summer Olympics medal table|35]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1968}} || 31 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1968 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1972}} || 59 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1972 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1976}} || 44 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1976 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1980}} || 47 || 0 || 1 || 1 || '''2''' || [[1980 Summer Olympics medal table|31]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1984}} || 42 || 0 || 1 || 0 || '''1''' || [[1984 Summer Olympics medal table|33]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1988}} || 61 || 0 || 0 || 0 || '''0''' || [[1988 Summer Olympics medal table|\u2013]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{GamesName|SOG|1992}} || 58 || 1 || 1 || 0 || '''2''' || [[1992 Su