2/olympic-gold-medal-rower-from-donegal/|title=Olympic gold medal rower from Donegal?|date=8 February 2013|accessdate=8 February 2013}}</ref>\n\n=== Medallists ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n!style=\"width:6em\"| Medal\n!style=\"width:12em\"| Name\n!style=\"width:12em\"| Games\n! Sport\n! Event\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Pat|O'Callaghan}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1928}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's hammer throw\n\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Bob|Tisdall}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1932}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1932 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's 400 metre hurdles\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Pat|O'Callaghan}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1932}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1932 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's hammer throw\n\n|-\n| {{silver medal}} || {{sortname|John|McNally|John McNally (boxer)}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1952}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 1952 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's bantamweight\n\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Ronnie|Delany}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1956}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1956 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's 1500 metres\n|-\n| {{silver medal}} || {{sortname|Fred|Tiedt}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1956}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 1956 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's welterweight\n|-\n| {{bronze medal}} || {{sortname|John|Caldwell|John Caldwell (boxer)}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1956}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 1956 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's flyweight\n|-\n| {{bronze medal}} || {{sortname|Freddie|Gilroy}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1956}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 1956 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's bantamweight\n|-\n| {{bronze medal}} || {{sortname|Anthony|Byrne|Anthony Byrne (boxer)}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1956}} 