g|Format=d}} \n | gold_4  = 0  | silver_4  = 2  | bronze_4  = 0  | name_4  = {{GamesSport|Sailing|Format=d}} \n | gold_5  = 0  | silver_5  = 1  | bronze_5  = 0  | name_5  = {{GamesSport|Rowing|Format=d}} \n | gold_6  = 0  | silver_6  = 0  | bronze_6  = 1  | name_6  = {{GamesSport|Equestrian|Format=d}} \n}}\n\n== List of medallists ==\nThe following tables include medals won by athletes on OCI teams. All medals have been won at Summer Games. Ireland's best result at the Winter Games has been fourth, by [[Clifton Wrottesley]] in the [[Skeleton at the 2002 Winter Olympics|Men's Skeleton at the 2002 Games]] in [[Salt Lake City]]. Some athletes have won medals representing other countries, which are not included on these tables.<ref>{{cite news|first=Cronan|last=Scanlon|url=http://donegalnews.com/2013/02/olympic-gold-medal-rower-from-donegal/|title=Olympic gold medal rower from Donegal?|date=8 February 2013|accessdate=8 February 2013}}</ref>\n\n=== Medallists ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n!style=\"width:6em\"| Medal\n!style=\"width:12em\"| Name\n!style=\"width:12em\"| Games\n! Sport\n! Event\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Pat|O'Callaghan}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1928}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1928 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's hammer throw\n\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Bob|Tisdall}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1932}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1932 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's 400 metre hurdles\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Pat|O'Callaghan}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1932}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 1932 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Men's hammer throw\n\n|-\n| {{silver medal}} || {{sortname|John|McNally|John McNally (boxer)}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1952}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 1952 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's bantamweight\n\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Ronnie|Delany}} || {{Gam