G|1992}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 1992 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's bantamweight\n\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Michelle|Smith}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1996}} || [[File:Swimming pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Swimming at the 1996 Summer Olympics|Swimming]] || Women's 400 metre freestyle\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Michelle|Smith}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1996}} || [[File:Swimming pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Swimming at the 1996 Summer Olympics|Swimming]] || Women's 200 metre individual medley\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Michelle|Smith}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1996}} || [[File:Swimming pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Swimming at the 1996 Summer Olympics|Swimming]] || Women's 400 metre individual medley\n|-\n| {{bronze medal}} || {{sortname|Michelle|Smith}} || {{GamesName|SOG|1996}} || [[File:Swimming pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Swimming at the 1996 Summer Olympics|Swimming]] || Women's 200 metre butterfly\n\n|-\n| {{silver medal}} || {{sortname|Sonia|O'Sullivan}} || {{GamesName|SOG|2000}} || [[File:Athletics pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Athletics at the 2000 Summer Olympics|Athletics]] || Women's 5000 metres\n\n|-\n| {{silver medal}} || {{sortname|Kenny|Egan}} || {{GamesName|SOG|2008}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 2008 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's Light Heavyweight\n|-\n| {{bronze medal}} || {{sortname|Paddy|Barnes}} || {{GamesName|SOG|2008}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 2008 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's Light flyweight\n|-\n| {{bronze medal}} || {{sortname|Darren|Sutherland}} || {{GamesName|SOG|2008}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 2008 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Men's Middleweight\n|-\n| {{gold medal}} || {{sortname|Katie|Taylor}} || {{GamesName|SOG|2012}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.svg|25px]] [[Boxing at the 2012 Summer Olympics|Boxing]] || Women's lightweight \n|-\n|  {{silver medal}} || {{sortname|John Joe|Nevin}} || {{GamesName|SOG|2012}} || [[File:Boxing pictogram.sv