[Category:1998\u201399 in European association football leagues|Lith]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n|season           = 1998\u201399\n|dates            = \n|competition      = [[A Lyga]]\n|winners          = <!-- (th title) -->\n|relegated        = \n|continentalcup1  = \n|continentalcup1 qualifiers = \n|continentalcup2  = \n|continentalcup2 qualifiers = \n|continentalcup3  = \n|continentalcup3 qualifiers = \n|league topscorer = \n|biggest home win = \n|biggest away win = \n|highest scoring  = \n|matches          = \n|total goals      = \n|prevseason = [[1997\u201398 A Lyga|1997\u201398]]\n|nextseason = [[1999 A Lyga|1999]]\n|updated    = \n}}\nStatistics of [[A Lyga]] for the 1998\u201399 season. 13 teams participated and [[FK \u017dalgiris Vilnius]] won the championship.\n\n==Final table==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n\n|team1=\u017dAL|name_\u017dAL=[[FK \u017dalgiris|\u017dalgiris]]\n|team2=KAR|name_KAR=[[FK Kareda Kaunas|Kareda \u0160iauliai]]\n|team3=FBK|name_FBK=[[FBK Kaunas]]\n|team4=EKR|name_EKR=[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]\n|team5=INK|name_INK=[[FK Inkaras Kaunas|Inkaras]]\n|team6=ATL|name_ATL=[[FK Atlantas|Atlantas]]\n|team7=BAN|name_BAN=[[FK Banga Garg\u017edai|Banga]]\n|team8=NEV|name_NEV=[[FK Nev\u0117\u017eis|Nev\u0117\u017eis]]\n|team9=DAI|name_DAI=[[FK Dainava Alytus|Dainava]]\n|team10=\u017dAL2|name_\u017dAL2=[[\u017dalgiris-2 Vilnius|\u017dalgiris-2]]\n|team11=J\u0116G|name_J\u0116G=[[Kauno J\u0117geriai|J\u0117geriai]]\n|team12=LOK|name_LOK=[[Lokomotyvas Vilnius]]\n|team13=MAS|name_MAS=[[Mastis Tel\u0161iai|Mastis]]\n|win_\u017dAL=18|draw_\u017dAL=5|loss_\u017dAL=0|gf_\u017dAL=68|ga_\u017dAL=8|status_\u017dAL=C\n|win_KAR=18|draw_KAR=4|loss_KAR=1|gf_KAR=67|ga_KAR=11\n|win_FBK=18|draw_FBK=3|loss_FBK=2|gf_FBK=57|ga_FBK=14\n|win_EKR=12|draw_EKR=5|loss_EKR=6|gf_EKR=45|ga_EKR=20\n|win_INK=11|draw_INK=4|loss_INK=8|gf_INK=34|ga_INK=27\n|win_ATL=8|draw_ATL=4|loss_ATL=11|gf_ATL=34|ga_ATL=33\n|win_BAN=7|draw_BAN